Package: SimBu
Type: Package
Title: Simulation and Batch Correction for Single-Cell RNA-seq Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Steph Ritchie", email = "s.ritchie@sussex.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
)
Description: This package provides tools for simulating single-cell RNA-seq data and evaluating batch correction methods. It includes functions for data generation, simulation, and various batch correction techniques.
